history.text: classic animation from back in the day
Do you have a favorite character of all the toys?
I really like the idea of Buzz coming to the understanding that he is a toy as existential crisis. no favorites though. You?

The crisis of a seemingly tough guy arrogant character like Buzz is interesting since it can be compared to lots of people in real life in some sense. I liked Mr. Potato Head because he's bitter and it I found it funny watching him get dismembered from time to time
Ha, yeah. It's funny Tim Allen was so iconic as the tool man, it's interesting that he can be equally iconic as a cartoon.

awesome dude as well

real people aren't as good at using english properly
